generated_description: flow-eze, legally known as flow-eze company, based in rockford, illinois, is a diversified niche company specializing in product decoration and imprinting services. founded by william and alice mccarren, the company has evolved from its origins in chemical drain cleaners to offering a wide range of printing and assembly services. flow-eze provides high-precision pad printing on plastic, glass, and metal, as well as screen printing and hot stamping for industrial metal products and high-end cosmetic bottles. the company serves various industries, including medical devices, electronics, aerospace, craft brewing, distilling, retail, and promotional products, offering services from prototypes to large-scale production runs. flow-eze is committed to quality, customer service, and continuous improvement, leveraging three generations of experience to meet the unique needs of its diverse clientele.
